{"tid":2253904,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"指因不務正業才被阿仙奴棄用 《環球時報》追擊奧斯爾","createTime":"2020-10-22T12:57:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T13:14:19.000Z","uid":147522,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"01bfa27287dc735829886fb7b4dbf52ae49e2e6c","tid":2253904,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T12:57:03.000Z","msg":"奧斯爾批評被效力球會英超阿仙奴因政治因素被禁止上陣，事件繼續發酵。中國官媒《環球時報》在今日發文抨擊奧斯爾，借「阿仙奴球迷」指該名坐擁35萬鎊（約350萬港元）周薪的德國中場，是因「不務正業」才被貶，再順勢抨擊前香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒借題發揮。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒在其個人社交網上就奧斯爾言論發表意見：「我對於阿仙奴球會將奧斯爾剔出英超聯賽大軍名單的決定感到失望，原因是他曾為維吾爾族人發聲，數以百計的維人現時被困在新疆集中營。球會將為公義發聲的球員打壓，實在是難以致信，令人驚訝這球會是否正向北京（政府）磕頭。」<br />\n<br />\n《環時》以「惡名昭彰的香港分裂主義者」來形容黃之鋒，並引述兵工廠主帥阿迪達的回應，後者強調奧斯爾不獲派上陣純粹是足球上的決定。《環時》亦指奧斯爾未能披甲，對中國的阿仙奴球迷來說並不意外，引述一名叫Zhao Yifan（音釋：趙一凡）表示，奧斯爾只是自食其果。趙說：「奧斯爾沒有努力爭取進步，落得如此結果只能怪他自己。沒有一家球會，會派上不專注在足球的球員上陣，只管每日都在社交媒體發佈錯誤與對抗球會的政治言論。英超無疑是高度商業的聯賽，他的言論有損球會的聲譽。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20201022/GYECLUGPGBHZZBQCKHASC3OGJA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20201022%2FGYECLUGPGBHZZBQCKHASC3OGJA%2F&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPVKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=cce3b8ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20201022%2FGYECLUGPGBHZZBQCKHASC3OGJA%2F&h=b4e04131\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20201022/GYECLUGPGBHZZBQCKHASC3OGJA/</a>"},{"pid":"be49db2b5e2c51a8eb29263d1b1f6325ada447fd","tid":2253904,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T12:58:46.000Z","msg":"官媒認證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"156003027931b7a8637706c07964c68eab01c56a","tid":2253904,"uid":147522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T12:59:25.000Z","msg":"「奧斯爾沒有努力爭取進步，落得如此結果只能怪他自己。沒有一家球會，會派上不專注在足球的球員上陣，只管每日都在社交媒體發佈錯誤與對抗球會的政治言論。英超無疑是高度商業的聯賽，他的言論有損球會的聲譽。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b13e3791b21a5a3a2d810e96835300142d2cbf3f","tid":2253904,"uid":136226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T12:59:34.000Z","msg":"個支那球迷收皮啦<br />\n咩不務正業呀 有冇睇過奧斯爾落場嘅表現㗎<br />\n場場都同你跑足啊 支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0ef1e7e2863247a735b2cda1f6d456c93773f7","tid":2253904,"uid":51583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:00:15.000Z","msg":"要有一個OFFICIAL既TWITTER比大家推<br />\n全世界推"},{"pid":"002e51653b5399e174dc923e54b529f462248922","tid":2253904,"uid":76958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:00:23.000Z","msg":"阿狗果然係流住紅色嘅血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40db18baa592504ba8d51930b9efda9727100531","tid":2253904,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:01:40.000Z","msg":"加速師真係唔係浪得虛名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffe4d0e3a8999189cd65e8617886d54081ba7b57","tid":2253904,"uid":230672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:01:56.000Z","msg":"笑撚死 惡魔之吻<br />\n阿仙奴正式變成阿森納<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b40ee259ec9a7ea83775dfe80531f87c680c2f16","tid":2253904,"uid":185656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:03:16.000Z","msg":"支那狗都係睇返支超啦<br />\n學咩人祟洋"},{"pid":"0b1188ed0e122be51a75e2d929c72515c6de7bac","tid":2253904,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc0ef1e7e2863247a735b2cda1f6d456c93773f7","tid":2253904,"uid":515